data.name: Plugin
data.desc:
This command can be used by an operator to activate/deactivate plugins
reload them and more.

data.name: ChallengeClear
data.desc: Clears all challenges

data.name: Hint
data.desc: Gives you (a) hint(s) to the question(s).

data.name: Question
data.desc:
Generates a random question correspongind to your entered subject.
You can answer a question qith the ID provided.
usageInstruction:
CLIL Hilfeseite. Sie brauchens, wir habens!
!question *</SUBJECT> </DIFFICULTY>*
__SUBJECT:__
  /TBD     - TO BE DONE!.

__DIFFICULTY:__
  /0      - a rather simple question that everyone should be able to solve
  /1     - a more difficult question. More test oriented
  /2     - TO BE DONE

__Example:__   !challenge hwe 1

data.name: Change
data.desc:
With this command an operator can change the: gToken, gCGame, gCPrefix, mChannelID, mPLaylistLimit
mAudioBuffer
usageInstruction:
CLIL Hilfeseite. Sie brauchens, wir habens!
!solution *</TOKEN>*
__TOKEN:__
  /TOKEN_STRING     - The token of the question!.

__Example:__   !solution blablalbablalbablablabla

data.name: Answer
data.desc:
Checks wether your answer is true or false. 
If your answer is true, points will be added to your point list!

data.name: Submit
data.desc:
Opens the 4-Gewinnt Bot Question Forms.
You can submit your own questions!

data.name: Solution
data.desc:
Shows the solution of the question.
Note: For every solution that you request, points will be removed from your score.
Once your point count reaches 0 you will not be able to request any solutions.

!solution *</TOKEN>*
